mindmap
  root((AI Decision Framework))
    The Problem
      Wrong people in the room
      Technical decisions stay siloed
      Business problems emerge late
    Framework Structure
      Stakeholders at top
      Decision rows below
      Columns capture trade-offs
    What It Is Not
      Not a prescriptive checklist
      Not one-size-fits-all
      Not just for enterprises
    Science-First Mindset
      Experimental thinking
      Small decisions and iteration
      Documented reasoning
    Side Benefits
      Cross-functional education
      Surfaces hidden risks
      Builds organizational buy-in
    Core Principle
      Technical decisions carry business consequences
      Knowledge is distributed
      Structure the conversation